Class Dancer

  • java.lang.Object
    • problem2.Artist
      • problem2.MediaArtist

  • public class Dancer
extends MediaArtist
    This class extends the MediaArtist class and represents a dancer with given details--name, age, genre, awards received, and lists of movies, TV series and other multimedia work the dancer is involved in. This class leaves room for additional methods for the dancer.
